                        https://www.ft.com/
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row border-bottom">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 fs-5 text-bold">
                        <p>Certificate issue date: </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-9 fs-5">
                        <time datetime="2023-04-11 00:00" id="dateIssued">11th April 2023</time>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row border-bottom">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 fs-5 text-bold">
                        <p>Certificate expiry date: </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-9 fs-5">
                        <time datetime="2024-04-11 00:00" id="dateExpired">11th April 2024</time>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row border-bottom">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 fs-5 text-bold">
                        <p>Certificate status: </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-9 fs-5">
                        <span id="accreditationStatus"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row border-bottom">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 fs-5 text-bold">
                        <p>Platform: </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-9 fs-5">
                        Desktop and Mobile
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3"></div>
                <h2>Certification</h2>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                        <p>To achieve certification each undergoes a manual technical compliance review against WCAG 2.1
                            to level AA.</p>
                        <p>The underwent both a technical compliance audit and robust end to end testing by users with a
                            wide range of disabilities including blind, low vision, dyslexia, colour blindness, mobility
                            impairments, learning difficulties, Deaf, Asperger and anxiety and panic disorder.</p>
                        <p>All testing is carried out in line with relevant platform specific guidelines, and where
                            applicable, conforms with The Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No.
                            2) Accessibility Regulations 2018. Testing also conforms to Section 508 of the Americans
                            with Disabilities Act (ADA)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="KnownIssues">

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-KnownIssues">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#flush-KnownIssuesTarget" aria-expanded="false"
                                aria-controls="flush-KnownIssuesTarget">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>&emsp;Known Accessibility Issues
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="flush-KnownIssuesTarget" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                            aria-labelledby="flush-KnownIssues" data-bs-parent="#KnownIssues">

                            <div class="row border-bottom mb-3">
                                <div class="col-12-lg">
                                    <h3>List of issues</h3>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Live Blog: Images of graphs may not pass colour contrast ratios due to being supplied by 3rd party and reliant on important data and informaiton.</li>
										<li>Climate Capital: The images and graphs have colour contrast ratio issues and non-text content. Financial Times is investigating the issues, and these will be addressed at a later date.</li>
										<li>Opinion: There is no text alternative for the graphs on this page. Financial Times is investigating the issues, and these will be addressed at a later date.</li>
										<li>Global Issue: Adverts and partner content may not be accessible which is out of their control. Financial Times is investigating the issues, and these will be addressed at a later date.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

